name: Russian Twist
description: Rotate torso side to side while holding weight. Legs slightly above the ground.

name: Side Plank
description: Hold body sideways supported on forearm.

name: Incline Barbell Bench Press
description: Press barbell on an incline bench.

name: Low-to-Hight Cable Fly
description: Pull cables upward in an arc to chest height.

name: Flat Barbell Bench Press
description: Press barbell from chest on flat bench.

name: Flat Dumbbell Press
description: Press dumbbells from chest on flat bench.

name: Pec Dech Machine
description: Bring arms together in front of chest.

name: Decline Barbell Bench Press
description: Press barbell on a decline bench.

name: Dumbbell Alternating Curl
description: Curl dumbbells one at a time.

name: Tricep Pushdown
description: Push rope or bar down on cable.

name: Wrist Curl
description: Flex wrists with barbell or dumbbells.

name: Arnold Press
description: Rotate dumbbells overhead from chest level.

name: Reverse Pec Deck
description: Move arms backward on the machine.

name: Bent-Over Dumbbell Reverse Fly
description: Lift dumbbells out to sides while bent.

name: Face Rope Pull
description: Pull rope attachment to face height.

name: Upright Row
description: Pull barbell or dumbbells up to chest.

name: Prone Y Raise
description: Raise arms in Y shape while lying face down.

name: Scapular Depression (Lat Pulldown Hold)
description: Pull shoulders down against the bar.

name: Dumbbell Row
description: Row dumbbell to torso from bent position.

name: Barbell Deadlift
description: Lift barbell from floor to standing.

name: Hyperextension
description: Extend torso upward on hyper bench.

name: Good Morning
description: Bend forward with barbell on back.

name: Side-Lying Leg Raise
description: Lift top leg upward while lying sideways.

name: Cable Hip Abduction
description: Move leg outward with cable strap to your ankle.

name: Banded Lateral Walks
description: Step sideways with resistance band around your ankles.

name: Glute Bridge
description: Push hips upward with weight or your bodyweight.

name: Romanian Deadlift
description: Lower and raise barbell with hips hinging.

name: Copenhagen Plank
description: Hold side plank with inner thigh support.

name: Clamshell
description: Open knees outward with band while lying.
